WEBVTT

00:04.240 --> 00:07.391
Rio de Janeiro is famous for its picturesque beaches...

00:09.512 --> 00:11.495
...as well as the enormous statue...

00:11.630 --> 00:16.394
...called Christ the Redeemer, 93 feet tall.

00:17.291 --> 00:18.515
The figure is perched...

00:19.194 --> 00:21.452
...atop the peak of Corcovado mountain,...

00:22.347 --> 00:24.357
...watching over the city below.

